<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٦٦ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ، حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُنْكَدِرِ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ جَابِرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ <span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(هَلْ اتَّخَذْتُمْ أَنْمَاطًا)</span>.<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> يَا رَسُولَ اللَّهِ وَأَنَّى لَنَا أَنْمَاطٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنَّهَا سَتَكُونُ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
